text: Filipe Bezugo (born 10 November 1980) is a Portuguese gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Portugal Category:Gymnasts at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Funchal
